# Windows / MacOS
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# --- Package Manager (only manifest is needed) ---
/[Pp]ackages/manager/
/[Pp]ackages/*/
!/[Pp]ackages/manifest.json
!/[Pp]ackages/packages-lock.json

# --- Crashlytics (Firebase) ---
Crashlytics/

# --- Unity Asset Store tools ---
/[Aa]ssets/AssetStoreTools*

# --- Autogenerated Asset meta files (Git LFS tip: keep them!) ---
# Do NOT ignore *.meta files – they are essential.
# If you use Git LFS, track large binary files but still keep .meta.

# Unity’s own .gitignore often adds:
*.log
*.unitypackage

# Visual Studio cache
*.vs/
*.vscode/